location.fullValue: Jefferson - Basement Plan, Reflections at Stonehouse : Villa Homes

data.description: Welcome home! Bright 2-story single-family home on 12th fairway in Orchard Hill at Stonehouse. Lots of storage! Recessed lighting! Front porch opens to foyer, generous dining room opens to kitchen. Pull into one of the bays of 2-car garage and enter thru the laundry room with a sink. Plantation shutters grace all windows on first level. 1st FL PBR with ensuite (DBL vanity, jetted tub), his/hers WIC and sitting space. DBL-sided fireplace warms living room & breakfast area. Transition to a cozy screened in porch equipped with ceiling fan and shades. 2nd FL loft/sitting area with built-ins. 2 bedrooms adjoin by pocket door jack-and-jill bath (rear balcony). Home office with step down media room/man cave. Amenities included with POA: Orchard Hill has its own pool and park! Plus main Stonehouse amenities: 2nd pool, gym, hiking trails, boat ramp to Mill Pond, RV storage, tennis and soccer, discounted golf. Special Services: landscaping (lawn, hedge, edge, & irrigation). 24 hour security!
